5703007237.html\"></div><div><article class=\"hascomments\" data-page=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/dcg1665703007237.html\" id=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/dcg1665703007237.html\"><main role=\"main\"><article aria-labelledby=\"ariaid-title1\" class=\"dita\" id=\"dcg1665703007237\" role=\"article\">\n<h1 class=\"title topictitle1\" id=\"ariaid-title1\">\n      $display </h1>\n<div class=\"body conbody\" id=\"dcg1665703007237___display_259412\"><p class=\"shortdesc\">Return the name of the current display device translation table.\n </p>\n<section class=\"section refsyn\" id=\"dcg1665703007237__topic_d82034e1_d82035e1_d82036e1\">\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"dcg1665703007237__p_d82037e1_d82038e1_d82039e1\">\n<var class=\"keyword varname\">vDdt</var>=<span class=\"keyword cmdname\">$display</span>\n</p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"dcg1665703007237__topic_d54102e1_d54103e1_d54104e1_d54105e1_d54106e1\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d571355e69\">\n                       \n Return Values\n </h2>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"dcg1665703007237__p_d82043e1_d82044e1_d82045e1\">Name of the device translation table being used for display.</p>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table class=\"table\" count-columns=\"3\" id=\"dcg1665703007237__table_d8321e1_d8322e1_d8323e1\"><caption><span class=\"table--title-label\">Table 1. </span><span class=\"title\">Values commonly returned by <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">$procerror</span> following\n                  <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">$display</span>\n</span></caption><colgroup><col/><col/><col/></colgroup><thead class=\"thead\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"dcg1665703007237__table_d8321e1_d8322e1_d8323e1__entry__1\">\n Value\n </th>\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"dcg1665703007237__table_d8321e1_d8322e1_d8323e1__entry__2\">\n<p class=\"p\">Error constant</p>\n</th>\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"dcg1665703007237__table_d8321e1_d8322e1_d8323e1__entry__3\">\n Meaning\n </th>\n</tr>\n</thead><tbody class=\"tbody\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"dcg1665703007237__table_d8321e1_d8322e1_d8323e1__entry__1\">\n -33\n </td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"dcg1665703007237__table_d8321e1_d8322e1_d8323e1__entry__2\">\n<p class=\"p\">\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">&lt;UGENERR_BATCH_ONLY&gt;</code>\n</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"dcg1665703007237__table_d8321e1_d8322e1_d8323e1__entry__3\">\n Statement not allowed in batch mode. Use a test on <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">$batch</span> to avoid this.\n </td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"dcg1665703007237__table_d8321e1_d8322e1_d8323e1__entry__1\">\n -1401\n </td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"dcg1665703007237__table_d8321e1_d8322e1_d8323e1__entry__2\">\n<p class=\"p\">\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">&lt;UPROCERR_PROMPT&gt;</code>\n</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"dcg1665703007237__table_d8321e1_d8322e1_d8323e1__entry__3\">\n Prompted field not valid.\n </td>\n</tr>\n</tbody></table></div>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"dcg1665703007237__topic_d54107e1_d54108e1_d54109e1_d54110e1_d54111e1\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d571355e159\">\n                       \n Use\n </h2>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"dcg1665703007237__p_d82049e1_d82050e1_d82051e1\">Allowed in all component types.</p>\n</section>\n</div>\n</article></main></article>\n</div></div><div class=\"contentPlaceholder\" style=\"height: 500px;\"><div class=\"contentContainer zDocsSideBoxes\"><div><h5 aria-level=\"5\" class=\"css-g931ng\">Related Links</h5><ul><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/zkc1665703224453.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>$DISPLAY</a><p>Specify a translation table for display in character-based user interface (CHUI).</p></li><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/zbn1665702665252.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>$keyboard</a><p>Return or set the current keyboard translation table.</p></li><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/ejp1665702655701.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>Device Translation Tables</a><p>Device translation tables handle output to screens and printers. They map Uniface logical functions onto device functions, making it possible for Uniface to support a wide variety of hardware platforms, including their output devices.</p></li></ul></div></div></div></div><div class=\"bottomFeedback\"><div aria-labelledby=\"bottomFeedbackText\" class=\"bottomFeedbackContent\" role=\"group\"><span class=\"bottomFeedbackText\" id=\"bottomFeedbackText\">Was this topic helpful?</span><div class=\"bottomFeedbackButtonGroup\"><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_2526737\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-up\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-up\"></use></svg><span>Like</span></a><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_2526737\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-down\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-down\"></use></svg><span>Dislike</span></a></div></div></div><div style=\"position: fixed; bottom: 170px; right: 70px; cursor: pointer; transition-duration: 0.2s; transition-timing-function: linear; transition-delay: 0s; z-index: 3; opacity: 0; visibility: hidden; transition-property: opacity, visibility;\"><button aria-label=\"Scroll to top\" class=\"zDocsScrollTopBtn\" data-tooltip-content=\"Scroll to top\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsBackToTopToolTip\" id=\"zDocsScrollToTop\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-next\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-next\"></use></svg></button></div></body></html>", "text": "$display Add to My Topics Add selected topic and subtopics Add Topic & Subtopics with topic head Add entire publication Watch Download PDF Save selected topic Save selected topic and subtopics Save entire publication Share Email Link Copy Link Feedback Last Updated Dez 20, 2024 Summarize Uniface 10.4 $display Return the name of the current display device translation table. vDdt = $display Return Values Name of the device translation table being used for display. Table 1. Values commonly returned by $procerror following $display Value Error constant Meaning -33 <UGENERR_BATCH_ONLY> Statement not allowed in batch mode. Use a test on $batch to avoid this. -1401 <UPROCERR_PROMPT> Prompted field not valid. Use Allowed in all component types. Related Links $DISPLAY Specify a translation table for display in character-based user interface (CHUI). $keyboard Return or set the current keyboard translation table. Device Translation Tables Device translation tables handle output to screens and printers. They map Uniface logical functions onto device functions, making it possible for Uniface to support a wide variety of hardware platforms, including their output devices. Was this topic helpful? Like Dislike"}